        <briefdescription>
<para>Recomputes cached metrics if needed. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>If `needsUpdate_` is true and the history is non-empty, this function updates `lastWorkTime_`, `lastWaitTime_`, `avgFrameTime_` and `avgFps_` based on the current contents of `history_` and then clears the flag.</para>
